    </statBases>
    <description>A battery enhanced with uranium. It has exceptional capacity and efficiency, but loses 1% efficiency for every 1째C it is above 20째C (or every 1.8째F above 68째F). Uranium batteries will not break down, but can short-circuit in rain and generate heat. They will also violently explode if destroyed. \n\nCapacity: 1500 Wd\nEfficiency: 90%</description>
    <descriptionHyperlinks>
      <ThingDef>Battery</ThingDef>
      <ThingDef>Battery_Silver</ThingDef>
